ds to a model of GRB jets with systematic\nlongitudinal variation of Lorentz factor which may have specific observational\nsignatures both in the prompt and the afterglow emission.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Jul 2007 16:14:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 6 Jul 2007 11:15:27 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 22 Sep 2007 18:18:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
