hannel with M>1 antennas at each node. Fifth, we\ncharacterize the degree of freedom benefits from cognitive sharing of messages\non the 3 user interference channel.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Jul 2007 15:26:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 11 Jul 2007 01:28:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-07-13"}
